function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(S_CONV_LITANYDOOROPEN, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(S_CONV_LITANYDOOROPEN)
	
	--Hide Sign Gizmo, Enable and destory Switch version
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idActorGizmo)
	for i, idScroll in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_DoorScrolls")) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idScroll, false)
		Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(idScroll, idActorPlayer)
	end
	
	--Open Door
	Hydra.EventSend("DRLG_Door_Lock_Sigil_Deactivate_01")
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_BossDoorGroup")[1], false)

end

	T_AngrySpirits1 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_BossAngrySpirits1")
	T_AngrySpirits2 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_BossAngrySpirits2")
	T_AngrySpirits3 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_BossAngrySpirits3")
	
--	Spawning sessions for Scholar Ghosts
	for id, i in ipairs(T_AngrySpirits1) do

	end

	end

	end 
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	--Swap BookPyre to Burning Actor
	idBookPreburn = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_BookPile")[1]
	idBookBurn = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_BurnPile")[1]
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idBookPreburn)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idBookBurn)
	
	--Ghost Boss manefestation
	T_AllAngrySpirits = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_BossAngrySpirits")
	ID_ABBOT = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_AbbotActor")[1]	
	
	--Play Ghost Boss screaming SFX
	Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idBookBurn, SFX_BOSSScream)
	
	for id, i in ipairs(T_AllAngrySpirits) do	
		-- Spawn All Ghosts
		Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(i)
	end
	
	
	T_AllAngrySpririts_Spawned = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Orbei_BossAngrySpirits_Spawned")
	ID_GhostForScream1 = T_AllAngrySpririts_Spawned[1]
	ID_GhostForScream2 = T_AllAngrySpririts_Spawned[2]
	
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_GHOST5, idActorPlayer)
	
	
	--Abbot Anim Override for Outro
	Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idActorNPC, "AnimKey_AnimSet_Outro")
	Hydra.Wait(3)
	
	--Ingite Abbot VFX
	Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorNPC, "actor_dot_fire_large")
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	
	
	Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorNPC, "environmentVFX_fire_wild_medium_tall")
	Hydra.ActorPlaySound(ID_GhostForScream1, MaleScream_SFX)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySound(ID_GhostForScream2, FemaleScream_SFX)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySound(ID_GhostForScream1, SFX_BOSSSpawn)
	
	for id, i in ipairs(T_AllAngrySpririts_Spawned) do
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(i, idActorNPC, "NPC_RUN", false)
	end

	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorNPC, FX_GHOSTEXPLOSION)
	for id, i in ipairs(T_AllAngrySpririts_Spawned) do
		Hydra.ActorDelete(i)
	end
	
	--Destroy BookPyre
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idBookBurn) then
		Hydra.ActorDisable(idBookBurn)
	end
	
	idBookBurnt = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("OST_Orbei_BurntPile")[1]
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idBookBurnt)
	
	--Spirit Boss Activates, fog walls enabled
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(S_LEVELAREA_SPIRIT_BOSS)
	
	--Play Boss Music
	--Hydra.MusicOverride("CSD_Step_Orbei_OrbeiMonastery", "Music_Boss_Orbei_Phase1")

end
